description:
The CEO is back and gives us a recap of his weekend. Along with this, Steve Harvey is the #1 TV celebrity on social media. Tonight Last O.G. Standing airs on TBS and Cedric The Entertainer talks to the show about it. Real Housewives of Atlanta has their reunion and hear Carla's take and more!
